content.body:
### Shop 185/60R16 Tire Size
Do you drive a Toyota Yaris, Scion iA, or Volkswagen Cabriolet? Chances are you’re driving on 185/60R16 tires, and your vehicle might’ve left the factory with a set of Toyo Proxes A27 tires attached.

Popular vehicles
2017-2020 Toyota Yaris
2016 Scion iA
1986 Volkswagen Cabriolet

All-season tires are built to perform year-round, making them a common choice for drivers. Check out the [Yokohama Avid Ascend GT](https://simpletire/com/brands/yokohama-tires/avid-ascend-gt), Nexen N Priz AH8, and Toyo Extensa A/S II if you’re looking for a set of 185/60R16 tires that are built to perform in dry, wet, and light winter weather conditions.

While all-season tires do perform well year-round, they might struggle in heavier ice, slush, and snow. Fortunately, winter tires are engineered to perform in these conditions so take a look at the [Pirelli Cinturato Winter](https://simpletire.com/brands/pirelli-tires/cinturato-winter) or Toyo Observe GSI-5 if you want extra traction in winter weather.

Whether you drive a Toyota Yaris, Scion iA, or something else, SimpleTire has a set of 185/60R16 tires that meets your needs at a great price!
